Maddox Hatter.

156
00:06:47.407 --> 00:06:49.159
The once kindhearted inventor

157
00:06:49.242 --> 00:06:51.953
went so mad searching
for the pocket watch.

158
00:06:52.037 --> 00:06:54.831
the Queen of Hearts
banished him to the Isle of the Lost.

159
00:06:54.914 --> 00:06:56.458
But now he's out.

160
00:06:56.541 --> 00:07:00.128
determined to find his prize
and to get his revenge.

161
00:07:00.211 --> 00:07:01.212
[chuckles mischievously]

162
00:07:01.296 --> 00:07:04.591
Lucky for him.
this kitten is ready to play.

163
00:07:06.343 --> 00:07:08.219
Oh. hello. Maddox.

164
00:07:08.303 --> 00:07:09.554
Anything new?

165
00:07:09.638 --> 00:07:14.768
After all these years searching.
my Oraculum has found the pocket watch.

166
00:07:14.851 --> 00:07:15.977
Of course!

167
00:07:16.061 --> 00:07:17.062
[Chessy] Indeed.

168
00:07:17.145 --> 00:07:20.315
It seems the Queen of Hearts
has it in her vault.

169
00:07:20.398 --> 00:07:23.234
That means... it's here!

170
00:07:24.361 --> 00:07:25.654
In Wonderland.

171
00:07:25.737 --> 00:07:29.240
Just imagine what you could do
with the pocket watch.

172
00:07:29.324 --> 00:07:31.117
Change the past. the future...

173
00:07:31.660 --> 00:07:34.162
Wonderland could finally be yours.

174
00:07:34.245 --> 00:07:36.581
-Ha!
-And the Queen of Hearts...

175
00:07:37.415 --> 00:07:38.500
[exhales]

176
00:07:38.583 --> 00:07:40.377
Oh. the Queen will be so...

177
00:07:40.460 --> 00:07:42.337
Dead? [chuckles evilly]

178
00:07:42.420 --> 00:07:44.506
[Maddox] No. Chessy. we need her alive.

179
00:07:44.589 --> 00:07:46.675
At least until we find that vault.

180
00:07:48.051 --> 00:07:51.554
Of course.
clever is as clever does. Right?

181
00:07:51.638 --> 00:07:52.972
No. kitten...

182
00:07:53.723 --> 00:07:56.184
Evil is as evil does!

183
00:07:56.726 --> 00:07:57.852
Dodo birds!

184
00:07:58.478 --> 00:08:02.399
Search the palace grounds.
the croquet gardens. Tulgey Woods.

185
00:08:02.482 --> 00:08:05.860
and every royal outpost
throughout Wonderland.

186
00:08:05.944 --> 00:08:07.987
Find me the pocket watch!

187
00:08:08.071 --> 00:08:11.032
-[dodos screeching]
-I'll deal with the Queen myself.

188
00:08:12.992 --> 00:08:15.412
Fly! I gave you wings for a reason!

189
00:08:15.995 --> 00:08:17.080
-[glass shattering]
-Ow! Ow!

190
00:08:17.163 --> 00:08:18.915
Watch it. you flying scrap heaps.

191
00:08:18.998 --> 00:08:21.209
[Maddox] Be my eyes over Wonderland

192
00:08:21.292 --> 00:08:23.712
and report back! [laughs evilly]

193
00:08:25.338 --> 00:08:27.966
[Chloe] Red. come on. we need to talk.

194
00:08:28.591 --> 00:08:30.969
Please tell me your morning
was at least better than mine.

195
00:08:31.052 --> 00:08:32.679
I pretty much woke up inside a cupcake.

196
00:08:32.762 --> 00:08:34.681
Well. my mom's even stricter than before.

197
00:08:34.764 --> 00:08:36.683
I mean. she followed me here to school.

198
00:08:36.766 --> 00:08:38.143
-Yikes.
-You know. when I got

199
00:08:38.226 --> 00:08:39.436
to meet my mom as a teenager.

200
00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:41.104
I thought that I understood her better.

201
00:08:41.187 --> 00:08:45.191
But seeing her today.
all proper and royal.

202
00:08:45.275 --> 00:08:47.402
it's like she's not even the same person.

203
00:08:47.485 --> 00:08:49.696
And you were there. Red.
You saw who Ella was.

204
00:08:50.572 --> 00:08:52.949
I just don't know how to feel
about my mom right now.

205
00:08:53.742 --> 00:08:55.869
I don't know how to feel about anything.

206
00:08:57.245 --> 00:09:00.832
I mean. look. Max Hatter is a VK now.

207
00:09:00.915 --> 00:09:02.333
I don't get it.

208
00:09:02.417 --> 00:09:04.961
His dad was
my mom's adviser and my friend.

209
00:09:05.045 --> 00:09:06.379
My only friend.

210
00:09:06.463 --> 00:09:07.547
And his son. Max...

211
00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:08.691
Let me show you the hat trick.

212
00:09:08.715 --> 00:09:10.484
If you guys don't like it.
I'm gonna be very upset.

213
00:09:10.508 --> 00:09:13.094
He wore button downs and bow ties.

214
00:09:13.178 --> 00:09:16.681
How does someone go
from that to pickpocketing? And why?

215
00:09:16.765 --> 00:09:19.184
[Chloe] Well. could be the crew
that he's hanging out with.

216
00:09:19.267 --> 00:09:22.353
Hazel's just as ruthless
as her father. Captain Hook.

217
00:09:22.437 --> 00:09:25.523
and always bossing
around her flunkies. the Smee twins.

218
00:09:25.607 --> 00:09:27.067
Who's that dude with the cards?

219
00:09:27.150 --> 00:09:28.401
[Chloe] That's Felix.

220
00:09:28.485 --> 00:09:30.236
Dr. Facilier's son.

221
00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:32.530
But the VKs aren't your crew anymore.

222
00:09:32.614 --> 00:09:34.074
Hate to break it to you. Red.

223
00:09:34.574 --> 00:09:37.285
-but you're an HK now.
-Would you like to see your future?

224
00:09:37.786 --> 00:09:38.787
-Bah!
-[girl exclaiming]

225
00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:40.413
[laughter]

226
00:09:40.497 --> 00:09:42.582
I'm... an HK now.

227
00:09:42.665 --> 00:09:43.750
Excuse me. [grunts]

228
00:09:44.876 --> 00:09:46.544
[♪ Magical stinger]

229
00:09:47.295 --> 00:09:48.296
[Red exclaims]

230
00:09:50.006 --> 00:09:51.257
I got it.

231
00:09:51.341 --> 00:09:53.259
It's okay. First rescue's free.

232
00:09:54.344 --> 00:09:56.096
My boy Luis always saves the day.

233
00:09:57.305 --> 00:09:58.431
[scoffs]

234
00:10:01.184 --> 00:10:02.268
[humming]

235
00:10:05.605 --> 00:10:08.108
Did you really think I wouldn't notice?

236
00:10:10.735 --> 00:10:13.029
That you're doing an amazing job!

237
00:10:13.113 --> 00:10:14.239
[laughs]

238
00:10:15.406 --> 00:10:16.741
[♪ Magical music playing]

239
00:10:23.915 --> 00:10:24.999
