241
00:10:29.921 --> 00:10:31.256
We should host a party.

242
00:10:31.339 --> 00:10:33.967
[gasps] Yes! For all of our friends!

243
00:10:34.050 --> 00:10:39.389
Ooh! We'll have
tea and cupcakes and raspberry tarts.

244
00:10:39.472 --> 00:10:44.102
Ooh. my favorite!
Ooh. and fireworks! Huge fireworks!

245
00:10:44.185 --> 00:10:46.771
-Oh. it will be...
-I love parties.

246
00:10:46.855 --> 00:10:48.064
[Queen of Hearts gasps]

247
00:10:48.148 --> 00:10:49.440
[♪ Dramatic music playing]

248
00:10:52.235 --> 00:10:55.029
Shame this one's such a snooze.

249
00:10:55.113 --> 00:10:56.197
[chuckles]

250
00:10:56.281 --> 00:10:57.615
