1981
01:28:17.334 --> 01:28:19.211
Those hedges got nothing on me.

1982
01:28:21.129 --> 01:28:22.172
I owe you one.

1983
01:28:23.799 --> 01:28:25.133
By my calculations.

1984
01:28:25.717 --> 01:28:26.718
